  "lyrics": "Are you going down the road again? Even though you know the end is near Even though you know the end is near Woah Woah Woah Woah Are you going down the road again? Woah My friend, are you going down the road again? Woah Woah I know you're going there, please be careful Woah Or you could lose your soul and the thing that makes you you My mama My mama Told me Keep your ass at home When it gets so late at night And the day It come from my tongue But you give it away If you're up all night Woah Woah I know you're going down that road again Woah No matter what I say Yeah, I know you're going down again Woah Woah Woah Don't get lost My friend, I said no Sometimes Yeah Don't look back To yesterday As I look forward All the way, yeah, all the way forward I look at myself In the mirror, see it clear in the mirror, see I ain't a checklist, oh So take that shit and run and go And you'll already know You can take that checklist on the road Woah Cause you're just going down again down that road Woah The only road you will ever know Woah Are you checking off your checklist? Down that unknown road that you're on Woah Nobody's looking for you down that road Please stay, don't go Anyone can see And you You shone it completely Yeah, you don't even care Bitch, if you're mad Are you fucking mad? Keep it to yourself Keep it to yourself, yeah",
